longBusinessSummary: Reo Plastics, Inc. provides plastic injection molding and related manufacturing services in Minnesota. The company offers plastic injection molding services, including engineering, plastic tooling, and automation services, as well as materials and plastic manufacturing equipment; and value added services, such as decoration, bonding/fastening, machining, and insertion services. It also provides plastic product assembly services comprising multiple assembly lines, contract manufacturing, verification testing, and shipping/distribution services; and lean manufacturing services. The company serves electronics/telecommunications, consumer/industrial, computer/business equipment, healthcare/medical, filtration/flow technology, and other markets. Reo Plastics, Inc. was founded in 1960 and is based in Maple Grove, Minnesota.
